  <description>
    <p>
      Odamex is a multiplayer-oriented DOOM port with a focus on classic DOOM gameplay.
      Maintaining the ability to play back vanilla demos, it is highly faithful to the original experience,
      while providing an enhanced experience with modern quality-of-life features and expanded modding capabilites.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>255 Player Maximum</li>
      <li>32-bit renderer</li>
      <li>MBF21 compatible</li>
      <li>
        Many multiplayer gamemodes:
        <ul>
          <li>Cooperative</li>
          <li>Deathmatch</li>
          <li>Team Deathmatch</li>
          <li>Capture the Flag</li>
          <li>Survival</li>
          <li>And more!</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>To use your own Timidity config file, use this command: <code>flatpak override net.odamex.Odamex --env=TIMIDITY_CFG=&lt;config location&gt;</code></p>
    <p><em>Note: The included version of Timidity does NOT support soundfonts, only GUS patches.</em></p>
    <p>A copy of DOOM, DOOM II, Freedoom, Hacx, REKKR, or Chex Quest is required. If you do not own DOOM, it can be purchased on GOG or Steam.</p>
  </description>
